the &quot;news&quot; page seems stale if i go there too often;
there are simply too many things i have seen before.<p>so i pretty much always look at the &quot;newest&quot; page,
and i might click two or three pages deep in that.<p>only occasionally do i click over to &quot;news&quot; to see
if there&#x27;s anything solid there i might have missed.<p>truly, both pages have become a bit unsatisfactory,
since one changes too quickly, the other too rarely.<p>-bowerbird
